    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入官方游戏群：1025057422</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重生回末日前，只有一台电脑，你可以拯救多少人呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319670/extras/0a28ce6fa6932069273a2d96120bb06b.webp?t=1754295671\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319670/extras/0a28ce6fa6932069273a2d96120bb06b.poster.avif?t=1754295671\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=200 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >末世囤货，大发横财</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次重生都获得新的成长点数，形成新的策略布局。在各种网站、论坛、闲聊中收集传闻，操纵股市、成为先知，获取大笔横财，提前囤积食物与材料、认识更强力的同伴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319670/extras/18c4dada7c3cea4f03d78b4c7d35b885.poster.avif?t=1754295671\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319670/extras/18c4dada7c3cea4f03d78b4c7d35b885.webm?t=1754295671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319670/extras/18c4dada7c3cea4f03d78b4c7d35b885.mp4?t=1754295671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建避难所，远程管理</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过建筑设计软件规划你的避难所，并安排同伴执行建造、探索、战斗、招募等任务，种植作物、研发技术，维护那些刁民的生存度，逐步打造一个能够抵御丧尸的新家园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319670/extras/5e7fd60fbc51a77cbb7baaaaac57381c.poster.avif?t=1754295671\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319670/extras/5e7fd60fbc51a77cbb7baaaaac57381c.webm?t=1754295671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319670/extras/5e7fd60fbc51a77cbb7baaaaac57381c.mp4?t=1754295671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >招募队友，规划排班</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在网络上发掘可招募培养的队友，战力爆炸的黑帮大小姐、探索力极强的探秘博主、建造学天才、顶级科学家，想方设法认识他/她，利用重生的优势，让他们成为你的员工，安排日程，一同维护避难所。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319670/extras/f9da8fd74bb9faf3ebe27ee311b26f20.poster.avif?t=1754295671\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319670/extras/f9da8fd74bb9faf3ebe27ee311b26f20.webm?t=1754295671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319670/extras/f9da8fd74bb9faf3ebe27ee311b26f20.mp4?t=1754295671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集传闻，聊聊人生</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >修复凤凰港各区域的网络，通过聊天软件联络那些你在网上认识的人物，从尸潮或人潮中解救大家，隔着网线，用那些你获得的秘闻，探寻属于每个人的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319670/extras/6238639bfb723eb661e55d5ddb502aab.poster.avif?t=1754295671\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319670/extras/6238639bfb723eb661e55d5ddb502aab.webm?t=1754295671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319670/extras/6238639bfb723eb661e55d5ddb502aab.mp4?t=1754295671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打打丧尸，捡捡垃圾</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >派出合适的人才，在危险的末世中探索珍贵资源，进入残忍的线上末日拍卖会、其他势力守护的食品仓库；提前预知尸潮的来临，生产武器防御避难所。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319670/extras/6b1f364ff87da564e2fa22f98c7973d0.webp?t=1754295671\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319670/extras/6b1f364ff87da564e2fa22f98c7973d0.poster.avif?t=1754295671\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=200 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >末世即绝境，但这次人生可以重来。</p>",
